name: Google Search, Web search index of 2 divas: Michael Jackson (MJ) and Farrah Fawsett (FF), June 27, 2009, USA
description: The polyshape file shows web searches (index) as of June 27, 2009, based on google search index for "Michael Jackson" and "Farrah Fawsett" by MSA. Searches for both rose dramatically, for Jackson its a more bi-coastal search while Fawsett search is more in the middle of the country. Google shows searches for only top 10 cities so the data is too small to show. Look elsewhere on the searches for the two icons/divas by state.
